{"tid":17333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"哇，林早蝕我屌你老母，個到屌完連巴呢頭做死狗","createTime":"2016-12-01T19:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T23:44:51.000Z","uid":7149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"884dd7a88142d3046b354522327a168e1645c2d8","tid":17333,"uid":7149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:24:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家真係咪撚信林狗呢條仆街仔</span></span><br />\n【新增內容】不少高登用戶過檔新成立「LIHKG討論區」，令行政總裁林祖舜非常頭痕。他接受本報訪問時指，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認為今次事件是有人有組織地，希望分化、打散香港一個有極高凝聚力的平台，「情況嚴重過鎅票。」</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n他表示，有人虛構前員工身入，去發散一些，他將要下台，以及iPhone上唔到高登官方App等不盡不實、抹黑的消息，認為「情況唔似係一個普通寫App人做」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11月29日屌撚完呢家黎做狗？唔好再諗住玩人情牌 我地明睇你仆街 今次你仲唔含家鏟.jpg</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161129/55981789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161129%2F55981789&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=c04c7022\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161129%2F55981789&h=4bb234e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161129/55981789</a>"},{"pid":"25333e319fb877d3653c46cf9b0476d5a041d3e0","tid":17333,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:27:23.000Z","msg":"傻鳩先會仲信佢\\<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/"},{"pid":"78c1225a051a1848e0a06203b3fa179033873d1a","tid":17333,"uid":7149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:28:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1c4f9fde78d0dc420c6e29dd705d751034d448b","tid":17333,"uid":7149,"like":0,"di